714257f-a.title: Manhattan: 69th Street (East) - 1st Avenue
714257f-a.text:
340-354 East 69th Street, south side, between Second and First
Avenues. The First Magyar Reform Church at 346 East 69th Street,
is in the center of the picture.
September 24, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
